ping\" Frequency: \"Daily at 2:00 AM\"\tCron expression generated\tUse simpler frequency if cron complex 6.6\tConfigure schedule details: • Actor: Instagram Comment Scraper • Input: Your JSON configuration • Frequency: 0 2 * * * (daily 2 AM)\tSchedule preview shows next runs\tYour optimized JSON input Timezone selection\tNext run time displayed correctly\tAdjust timezone if run time incorrect 6.7\tAdd webhook for data export: • URL: your-webhook-endpoint • Event: Run succeeded • Method: POST\tWebhook configuration saved\tYour webhook URL or integration endpoint\tWebhook test successful\tUse Zapier/Make webhook if no endpoint 📋 PHASE 7: BULK ACCOUNT PROCESSING SETUP Step\tExact Action Required\tExpected Screen/Result\tInput Data\tValidation Check\tTroubleshooting 7.1\tCreate account list spreadsheet: • Column A: Instagram Username • Column B: Account URL • Column C: Priority Level\tCSV with target accounts\t10-50 Instagram accounts URLs in format: instagram.com/[username]\tAll URLs valid and public\tRemove private/blocked accounts 7.2\tCreate master automat"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"[Content truncated — view full chat at source URL]"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=3ce61812-f1dc-4738-b311-95addbe98279","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=3ce61812-f1dc-4738-b311-95addbe98279"}]}]}]
